<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1152448>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Differential characters between genera Glyptosomus, Lalagetes and Phaylomerinthus: G. costipennis Schoenherr, 1847: A—ventrites, female; B—female sternite VIII; L. subfasciatus Boheman, 1842: C—ventrites, female; D—female sternite VIII; P. convergens (Voss, 1962): E—ventrites, female; P. cinereus Boheman, 1842: F—female sternite VIII; Scales bar:0.5 mm (B, D, F)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1152448/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1152452>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Apex of penis. A—Lalagetes andersoni sp. nov.; B—Lalagetes howdenorum sp. nov.; C—Lalagetes sarkae sp. nov.; D—Lalagetes subfasciatus Boheman, 1842; E—Lalagetes zitae sp.nov. Scales bar: 0.25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1152452/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1152460>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Lalagetes andersoni sp. nov. A—habitus, dorsal view, female; B—rostrum, female, dorsal view; C—rostrum, female, lateral view; D—protibia, female; E—aedeagus; F—spermatheca.Scales bars:1 mm (A), 0.5 mm (E) and 0.3 mm (F)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1152460/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1152464>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Lalagetes howdenorum sp. nov. A—habitus, dorsal view, female; B—rostrum, female, dorsal view; C—rostrum, female, lateral view; D—protibia, female; E—aedeagus; F—spermatheca.Scales bars:1 mm (A), 0.5 mm (E) and 0.3 mm (F)." ;
