    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Differential characters between genus Glyptosomus and genus Phaylomerinthus: G.costipennis Schoenherr, 1847: A—habitus, dorsal view, female; B—rostrum, female, dorsal view; C—protibia, male; P. cinereus Boheman, 1842: D— habitus, dorsal view, female; E—rostrum, female, dorsal view; F—protibia, female.Scales bar:1 mm (A, D)." ;
